.SS "Callback Information"
A pointer to the following structure is passed to each callback:
.sS
.iS
.ta .25i 1.1i
typedef struct
{
	int	\*Vreason\*L;
	XEvent	\*V* event\*L;
	int	\*Vclick_count\*L;
} XmArrowButtonCallbackStruct;
.iE
.sE
.wH .fi
.VL .75i 
.LI "\*Vreason\*O"
Indicates why the callback was invoked.
.LI "\*Vevent\*O"
Points to the \*LXEvent\*O that triggered the callback.
.LI "\*Vclick_count\*O"
This value is valid only when the reason is \*LXmCR_ACTIVATE\*O.
It contains the number of clicks in the last multiclick sequence
if the \*LXmNmultiClick\*O resource is set to \*LXmMULTICLICK_KEEP\*O,
otherwise it contains \*L1\*O.
The activate callback is invoked for each click if \*LXmNmultiClick\*O
is set to \*LXmMULTICLICK_KEEP\*O.
.LE 
.SS "Behavior"
XmArrowButtonGadget includes behavior from XmGadget.
Additional XmArrowButtonGadget behavior is described below:
.VL  
.LI "\*LBSelect\ Press\*O:"
Draws the shadow in the selected state and
calls the callbacks for \*LXmNarmCallback\*O.
.LI "\*LBSelect\ Click\ or\ BSelectRelease\*O:"
Draws the shadow in the unselected state.
If the pointer is within the ArrowButtonGadget,
calls the callbacks for \*LXmNactivateCallback\*O.
Calls the callbacks for \*LXmNdisarmCallback\*O.
.LI "\*LBSelect\ Press\ 2+\*O:"
If \*LXmNmultiClick\*O is \*LXmMULTICLICK_DISCARD\*O, this action does
nothing.
If \*LXmNmultiClick\*O is \*LXmMULTICLICK_KEEP\*O, this action
draws the shadow in the selected state and calls the callbacks for
\*LXmNarmCallback\*O.
.nL
.ne 7
.LI "\*LBSelect\ Release\ 2+\*O:"
If \*LXmNmultiClick\*O is \*LXmMULTICLICK_DISCARD\*O, this action does
nothing.
.P
If \*LXmNmultiClick\*O is \*LXmMULTICLICK_KEEP\*O, this action does the
following:
Increments \*Vclick_count\*O in the callback structure.
Draws the shadow in the unselected state.
If the pointer is within the ArrowButtonGadget, calls the
callbacks for \*LXmNactivateCallback\*O.
Calls the callbacks for \*LXmNdisarmCallback\*O.
.LI "\*LKSelect\*O:"
Draws the shadow in the selected state and
calls the callbacks for \*LXmNarmCallback\*O.
Arranges for the shadow to be drawn in the unselected state and
the callbacks for \*LXmNactivateCallback\*O and \*LXmNdisarmCallback\*O
to be called, either immediately or at a later time.
.LI "\*LKHelp\*O:"
Calls the callbacks for \*LXmNhelpCallback\*O if any exist.
If there are no help callbacks for this widget, this calls the help
callbacks for the nearest ancestor that has them.
.LI "\*L<Enter>\*O:"
Draws the ArrowButtonGadget shadow in its selected state if the
pointer leaves and re-enters the gadget while BSelect is pressed.
.LI "\*L<Leave>\*O:"
Draws the ArrowButtonGadget shadow in its unselected state
if the pointer leaves the gadget while BSelect is pressed.
.LE
